text: Ivana Karaja (born 1978, Berlin) is a German dance and pop musician. Her 2002 single, "She Moves (La La La)", was a major success worldwide. The track peaked at No. 42 in the UK Singles Chart in October that year, where she was billed simply as Karaja. Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:German musicians
